Query Data

Updated on : Mon Jan 30 13:33:04 2023

Setup

Install the package for the first time. devtools::install_github("ccb-hms/phonto")

library(phonto)
library(DT)
library(nhanesA)

Step 1: search tables

It can be search by certain variable.

1) Check variables constantancy

checkDataConst("DEMO_C","DEMO_D") |> DT::datatable()

2) Union Query

unionQuery(c("DEMO_B","DEMO_D"),c("RIDAGEYR","RIAGENDR")) |> DT::datatable()
#> [1] "SELECT  SEQN, RIDAGEYR, RIAGENDR FROM DEMO_B UNION SELECT SEQN, RIDAGEYR, RIAGENDR FROM DEMO_D"

3) Joint Query

jointQuery( list(BPQ_J=c("BPQ020", "BPQ050A"), DEMO_J=c("RIDAGEYR","RIAGENDR"))) |> DT::datatable()
